title: 820-00165 Fan Running Fast
message: I have 820-00165 Board, Macbook is running ok, just Fan is spinning at high speed. I don't know which asd to run on this model. I ran Hardware Test and it only shows Heatpipe 2 at 128 degree , Heatpipe outgoing air at 128 degree. No Corrosion near u5800, u5810, u5620. Any Suggestion please

title: 820-00165 Fan Running Fast
message:
Start trying known good LIO board/flex.
Next step, same thing for trackpad board/flex.

No ASD available since 2015...

title: 820-00165 Fan Running Fast
message: Yep rule out hardware first also disconnect the webcam cable to rule that out. If still same, pay close attention to if any sensor reads high in HW Monitor

title: 820-00165 Fan Running Fast
message: I did Install new IO Board and Flex, New flex cable for trackpad, No webcam connected, still it's in same condition

title: 820-00165 Fan Running Fast
message: Run HWMonitor and see which sensors report incorrectly will report 128 C when they should not
